{"tid":2478723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"營救理大案家長車司機被加控妨礙司法公正 保釋金大幅提升至十萬 需每日警署報到","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18a2334da395e1f697b920a6879735b2cffb4661","tid":2478723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14840&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=19e569f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14840</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #轉介文件<br />\n👤梁(23) #1120紅磡 #營救理大<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：危險駕駛<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月20日，在尖沙咀不遠處的暢通道南（地圖顯示現場為理工大學香港專上學院對開）涉嫌以危險方式駕駛一輛私家車。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：妨礙司法公正<br />\n(稍後補上)<br />\n===============<br />\n‼️控方表示有新增控罪，並申請撤銷被告擔保‼️<br />\n<br />\n✅法庭拒絕控方撤銷被告擔保的申請，唯被告需要遵守新修訂的保釋的條件✅<br />\n-保釋金提升至$100,000<br />\n-每天到警署報到<br />\n-其他條件依舊<br />\n<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年4月27日14:30在區域法院進行答辯程序，聆訊會用中文進行。<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示會保留不在場證據。"},{"pid":"cce1c6230cc570c7245caa0b594885920e8ca353","tid":2478723,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32b85ba73eacff595cfadfe007e97ce5131d3e7","tid":2478723,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"5b2c6dc7f8689876393b8721cf37afde28f2662c","tid":2478723,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" 